&lt;h2 id="org21f759b"&gt;&lt;span class="section-number-2"&gt;6.&lt;/span&gt; Outlook for 2022&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="outline-text-2" id="text-6"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
